    "content": "<p>Consider a system represented by the block diagram shown below. Which of the following signal flow graphs represent(s) this system? Choose the correct option(s).</p>\n<img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1mbezcumy/0e04eff2-2b38-4c48-8a30-3cc81495525a/06c147a0-3fa1-11f0-a491-e768f614f5b9/file-jaoe38c1mbezcumz.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1mbezcumy/0e04eff2-2b38-4c48-8a30-3cc81495525a/06c147a0-3fa1-11f0-a491-e768f614f5b9/file-jaoe38c1mbezcumz.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"GATE ECE 2025 Control Systems - Signal Flow Graph and Block Diagram Question 2 English\">",
